</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[189,1398,1395,1528]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Evers" authorityYear="1994" box="[319,438,1395,1421]" class="Insecta" family="Melyridae" genus="Nossibeus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[319,438,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Nossibeus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was erected for 
<taxonomicName authority="Fairmaire, 1880" authorityName="Fairmaire" authorityYear="1880" box="[635,985,1395,1421]" class="Insecta" family="Melyridae" genus="Laius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="politus">
<emphasis box="[635,788,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Laius politus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fairmaire L." box="[796,985,1395,1421]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="246" refId="ref11394" refString="Fairmaire L. 1880. Diagnoses de coleopteres de Nossi-Be. Le Naturaliste 2: 246." type="journal article" year="1880">Fairmaire, 1880</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Evers A. M. J." box="[1000,1140,1395,1421]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="169 - 181" refId="ref11356" refString="Evers A. M. J. 1994. Zur Phylogenie von Laius Guer., Collops Er. und der verwandten Gattungen. Entomologische Blatter fur Biologie und Systematik der Kafer 90: 169 - 181." type="journal article" year="1994">Evers 1994</bibRefCitation>
). After observation of this species, including its endophallic structure, it was clear that this species cannot be recognised as another species of the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Guerin-Meneville" authorityYear="1830" box="[538,603,1467,1492]" class="Insecta" family="Melyridae" genus="Laius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[538,603,1467,1492]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Laius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. In the present paper, 
<taxonomicName authority="Evers, 1994" authorityName="Evers" authorityYear="1994" box="[874,1145,1466,1493]" class="Insecta" family="Melyridae" genus="Nossibeus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[874,993,1466,1492]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Nossibeus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Evers A. M. J." box="[1002,1145,1466,1493]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="169 - 181" refId="ref11356" refString="Evers A. M. J. 1994. Zur Phylogenie von Laius Guer., Collops Er. und der verwandten Gattungen. Entomologische Blatter fur Biologie und Systematik der Kafer 90: 169 - 181." type="journal article" year="1994">Evers, 1994</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is treated as a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Guerin-Meneville, 1830" authorityName="Guerin-Meneville" authorityYear="1830" box="[336,692,1502,1528]" class="Insecta" family="Melyridae" genus="Laius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[336,401,1503,1528]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Laius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Guerin-Meneville F. E." box="[408,692,1502,1528]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="1 - 319" refId="ref11411" refString="Guerin-Meneville F. E. 1830. Crustaces, Arachnides et Insectes. In: Duperrey M. L. I. (ed.) Voyage autour du monde: execute par ordre du roi, sur la corvette de Sa Majeste, la Coquille, pendant les annees 1822, 1823, 1824, et 1825. Tome II. Part. 2 (1): 1 - 319. Arthus Bertrand, Paris. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 57936" type="journal article" year="1830">Guérin-Méneville, 1830</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(syn. nov.).
</paragraph>
